snippet.title: PAC-MAN Pizza Parlor
snippet.description:
PAC-MAN Pizza Parlor for PC: http://www.bigfishgames.com/download-games/8741/pacman-pizza-parlor/index.html

The PAC-MAN Pizza Parlor is open for business! When Cathy's father loses his memory, it's up to her to run the family pizza parlor. Fortunately, PAC-MAN is on the job to lend a helping hand. Help PAC-MAN and Cathy serve hungry customers through tons of tasty treats and delicious dishes in PAC-MAN Pizza Parlor, a fun Time Management game. With dozens of cool unlockables and equipment, you can customize your kitchen to your tastes!

  * Fast-paced gameplay
  * Intense action
  * Help PAC-MAN serve customers!
